_:N9ea9737a71d54e448bf6da854e5223f7 <http://schema.org/text> "The Health Equity in Health Protection Initiative (HEHPI) provides a central, external-facing platform that brings together UKHSA’s key health equity resources in one place. It helps ensure that data, research, and community insights are easier to find, use, and share." .
